Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I…chi…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.90,0:01:39.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Keigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:41.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:44.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't even said anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:46.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Mizuiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:47.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:49.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A pretty quiet morning, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:50.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:51.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:54.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see\Nwhat just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:56.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you ignoring it?\NWhy won't you mention it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:59.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, there was\Nsomeone here to see you, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:00.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are nice and easy\Nover here as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:26.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is around to scold you\Neven if you play kemari.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:30.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A far cry from life at the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:31.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:35.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:36.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:40.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:43.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is up to me where I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:47.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And if something did happen,\Nyou would help me, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:49.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop assuming\Nthings on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have things to do here,\Nmyself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Kenryu and Enryu?\NAren't they with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know about Kenryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:59.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:04.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you…become the head\Nof the Kasumiohji Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more conscious of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am well aware of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!\NThere is a good reason for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have class, so I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?!\NThat hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said listen to\Nwhat I have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool your head a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What could today's\Nmain dish be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Ichigo,\Nhe already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:51.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That was way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:56.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This has gone way past\Njust blowing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:58.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By herself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:02.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Looks like neither Kenryu\Nnor Enryu came with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did she come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:07.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing she got sick of living\Nat the mansion and ran away,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's Rurichiyo now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:18.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the trouble\Nin her clan is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,she's still the princess\Nof a noble family!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:23.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What if something unexpected\Nhappens to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Something unexpected?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:31.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,An inner tube!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What we need is an inner tube!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:38.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you come to the conclusion\Nof needing an inner tube?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:43.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well… Out of frustration,\NRurichiyo arrives at a certain pier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and jumps into the world\Nof the fisherman…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:50.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it'll take a long time\Nto explain, so stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:54.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,let's split up and find her\Nbefore anything terrible happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:55.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Right!\N– Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:58.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:20.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Man…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she became\Nhead of the clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,her knack for causing alarm\Nhasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:30.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:36.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She may have become\Nhead of the clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's still very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:41.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even imagine how heavy\Na responsibility that must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:44.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough to make her seek\Nrelief in the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We must not waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:49.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look for her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:50.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Right!\N– Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:54.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo's nowhere to be found!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Any idea where she might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:01.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,An idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, my, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:11.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering when you would\Ncome to pick her up, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling you\Nwould surely come soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:17.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so I didn't contact you,\Nbut what took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:19.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… No, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We…umm…just came to…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you think\Nof this place first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not want to!\NI am staying here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:33.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not want to go with\Nthat orange-headed man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:36.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep on being\Nunreasonable, you'll…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am telling you to leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:48.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying you're causing everyone\Ntrouble by coming here on a whim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the head of a noble clan,\Nyou know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am a selfish\Nhead of a clan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who knows nothing\Nof the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:56.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!\NI do not need your…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:03.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a bad mood\Nbecause you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That was not me!\NI assure you, I am not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:11.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:14.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it was Inoue?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:16.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was superb timing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:20.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.\NWant to go and eat something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:28.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That one…was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:38.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot get meals like this\Nunless you are in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my after-dinner tea\Nnot here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:44.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, waiter!\NBring me my tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:47.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!\NYou don't have to yell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:15.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If only she were this quiet\Nwhen she was awake as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:19.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were awake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:24.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…things must be\Ntough for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:28.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not particularly\Nneed your sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I left you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:41.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:45.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Kenryu?!\N– Kenryu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving the clan and\Ncoming to the World of the Living
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:51.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,is an outrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:56.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now wait…\NGive her a chance to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Was my scolding you\Nabout the kemari
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so hard for you to take?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what it was…\NShe…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:04.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about kemari is so wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:11.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:15.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a mountain of things\Nwe should do before playing kemari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is for me to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:19.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:21.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the reason you came here…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Kemari!\N– It's kemari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:28.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I keep telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:31.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, having a pastime\Nlike kemari is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:36.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have told you repeatedly,\Nuntil I turned blue in the face…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With the people alienating\Nthemselves from us now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:39.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,our priority is to repair relations
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:41.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with the leaders of\Nother noble families!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:43.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know about such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the head now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do what I believe in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That will not do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just this once, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:54.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I calm down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:56.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, do something about\Nthis pigheaded guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:01.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand how I feel,\Ndon't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:04.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh for crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Suit yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:16.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you saying that\Nyou oppose what I say
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how many times\NI tell you, Kenryu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We are about\Nthe only ones who can
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,persuade that stubborn\Nhead of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:26.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just call me stubborn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is my duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This resolve will not change,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:34.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it means I incur\Nyour anger or your distaste in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never liked you from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:39.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I hated you from way, way back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot obey me, then leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:01.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:03.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:06.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:08.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:11.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:21.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:26.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's Kenryu who's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,People connected with\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,appear to enjoy\Ncausing a commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:37.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rurichiyo didn't seem\Nmuch different from her usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:48.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Over here.\N– Pass, pass, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:53.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:58.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:03.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:27.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My skill is awesome, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:27.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:31.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing this isn't going\Nto solve anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:37.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That incident is at\Nthe root of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the domain of the Kasumiohji Clan\Nhas been unsettled,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:45.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and public safety is\Nsteadily growing worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The people have lost\Ntheir energy and spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,because of anxiety and distrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We are responsible for all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is when I came up with\Nthe idea of a kemari festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:02.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I recalled seeing something similar\Nin the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:06.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we could make\Nthe people happy with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:11.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, together with Shu,\NI worked out a plan, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you saying,\NLady Rurichiyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are telling you this\Nfor the good of{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:19.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you and the Kasumiohji Clan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am the head of this clan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:23.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me do as I wish!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That will not do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will keep on saying it\Nuntil you understand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:37.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kenryu would not\Nlisten to my plan at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:44.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the head of a clan should\Ndo what she believes is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but it is a bit tiresome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:55.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So you see, Rurichiyo\Nhas her reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:57.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we explain to Kenryu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't he listen to\Nwhat we have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:02.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But the way Kenryu looked,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:05.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,just trying to tell him is\Ngoing to be a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:09.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, there's no way\Nwe can tell Kenryu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if we don't know where he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:15.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Ichigo…\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:25.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:29.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:33.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo wasn't really serious\Nwhen she told you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:37.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you accept what she's saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:44.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo is focused\Non the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Regaining the trust of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:49.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and rebuilding the House is important too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:53.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe that in order to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:57.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,restore the Kasumiohji Clan,\Nwe need first to mend our relations
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:59.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with other noble families\Nand people with power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:02.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and work in tandem\Nwith them to govern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a matter of priorities!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One day,\Nwe will be able to have
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the type of government that\NLady Rurichiyo is seeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now,\Nwe don't have the luxury!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:13.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We must do what we must do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:16.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That, above all,\Nis for the good of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:23.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,neither of your views are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we going to do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:35.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's entirely my fault that I have not been able
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to convince Lady Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:46.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this,\NI will offer my life in exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute! Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:52.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop me, Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:54.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I must take responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:56.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! Don't rush things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:06.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki, let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:08.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Ishida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you would call\Ncompassion towards a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:14.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll watch him end his life\Nand report it to Rurichiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:14.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:17.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenryu, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will assist if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:26.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Only, I will be using an arrow\Nrather than a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Very well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Excuse me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:53.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong?\NYou look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:54.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kenryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:57.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find him?\NWhere was he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:01.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He…says he's going to\Ncommit suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:08.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenryu already left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:13.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not my concern\Nwhat happens to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:15.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right to say\Nsuch a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:20.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You made him protect you\Nin every way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but you won't consider\Nprotecting him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:26.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:52.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken…I mean Enryu!\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it will work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:22.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this the plan\Nyou came up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:25.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it is, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:29.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kenryu, go right ahead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shall assist if you wish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good grief, how melodramatic\Ncan you get?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not being melodramatic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:48.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Lady Rurichiyo still\Ndoes not change her mind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:52.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it is my duty to stop her,\Neven if it means taking my life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:57.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I found you people as I was\Nconsidering that thought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:59.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and wandering about the town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you weren't just\Nnearby by chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:05.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm begging you, Ichigo Kurosaki!\NHelp me out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:12.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this might be the best way\Nto persuade his master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:14.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:15.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:16.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:20.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Over here! Over here!\N– Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Hurry!\N– Kenryu! Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:31.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:33.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:35.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:38.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to live\Nwith this shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:41.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I would rather die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:42.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lady Rurichiyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:55.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think doing that is\Ngoing to make me happy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:00.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting my retainers\Nis my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:04.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Lady Rurichiyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:18.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:19.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:25.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My, my… I guess I will have to\Ngive in just this once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:28.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so happy that you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:32.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have to lose my life for\Nsomething as silly as kemari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As silly as kemari?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by\N"as silly as"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:42.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finding fault in my idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:48.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No…I…you know…\Na mere pastime like kemari is…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A mere pastime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:52.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…no, I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:54.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided not to\Ngive in after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:55.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:59.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said you would\Nagree with my view.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:02.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And who is the one who\Nstepped all over those feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And everything was going so well\Nwith everyone's cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Cooperation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Oh man…\N– Oh man…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:17.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So all this talk about committing\Nsuicide was to deceive me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:19.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable! Unforgivable!\NAbsolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped\Nnow that you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:25.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, kemari is out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:28.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand because\Nyou have never done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have, that's why I'm saying this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:33.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do something like that\Nbetter than you, Lady Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:36.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are going to talk like that,\Nlet us have a kemari competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:39.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall settle it with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:42.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us say the loser never\Nsays anything again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:44.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have it any other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:46.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How do things get this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:22.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Kuchiki, please accept this\Nas a small token of goodwill
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:24.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,from one noble family to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:26.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, but I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:29.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!\NThis is the elusive golden Chappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I went through great pains for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:32.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:35.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what is your request?\NI will hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:37.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you about\Nthis place, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.82,0:23:40.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my favorite optician.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:48.30,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,GINTONBO
